  "body_html": "<div>There is an increased risk of infection from encapsulated organisms, therefore the patient should recieve the following:<br /><br /><ul><li>Hib vaccine</li><li>Pneumococcal conjugate vaccine</li><li>Meningococcal vaccine</li></ul><br />In addition to the above patients are typically commenced on lifelong antibiotics and advised to have seasonal flu vaccination.</div>\n\n<div id=\"mybodylinks\"><table style='width:100%'><tr><td>Gloucester hospitals NHS trust</td><td style = \"float: right;width:115px;\"><button type=\"button\" style=\"\" id=\"link_like_18\" data-linkid=\"18\" data-rating=\"1\" class=\"rate-link btn btn-link\"><svg class=\"bi bi-hand-thumbs-up\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-hand-thumbs-up\"/></svg></button><span id=\"link_good_count_18\" class = \"link_good_count\" style=\"color:green; font-size:85%;\">0</span><button type=\"button\" style=\"\" id=\"link_dislike_18\" data-linkid=\"18\" data-rating=\"0\" class=\"rate-link btn btn-link\"><svg class=\"bi bi-hand-thumbs-down\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-hand-thumbs-down\"/></svg></button><span id=\"link_bad_count_18\" class = \"link_bad_count\" style=\"color:red; font-size:85%;\">0</span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.gloshospitals.nhs.uk/SharePoint1/Procedures%20and%20Guidelines/A0326.pdf\">Splenectomy</a></td></tr></table></div>\n\n<div id=\"mybodymedia\"></div>\n\n\n<div id=\"categorynum\">4</div>\n\n<div id=\"subcategorynum\">300</div>\n\n<div id=\"categoryname\">Microbiology</div>\n\n<div id=\"subcategoryname\">Clinical microbiology</div>\n<div id=\"mybody\">\n\n<div id=\"body_content\">\nThere is an increased risk of infection from encapsulated organisms, therefore the patient should recieve the following:<br /><br /><ul><li>Hib vaccine</li><li>Pneumococcal conjugate vaccine</li><li>Meningococcal vaccine</li></ul><br />In addition to the above patients are typically commenced on lifelong antibi